1. Install the Go 1.19 package on system

2. Check that mediator is set to 1.19

$ ls -la /usr/bin/go
lrwxrwxrwx   1 root     root          24 Dec 19 09:29 /usr/bin/go -> ../lib/go-golang

3. Check version

$ go version
go version go1.19.4 solaris/amd64

4. Go to the source tree

$ cd /usr/lib/golang/src

5. Run tests

$ bash run.bash --no-rebuild 2>&1 | tee /var/tmp/test.log.`mach`
